you've been afraid to speak.

358
00:21:20,112 --> 00:21:24,324
Use this time to rejoice and celebrate,

359
00:21:25,700 --> 00:21:27,661
for your time is short.

360
00:21:30,831 --> 00:21:32,749
I herald his beginning.

361
00:21:32,833 --> 00:21:35,627
I herald your end.

362
00:21:36,170 --> 00:21:37,546
I herald...

363
