377
00:22:58,127 --> 00:22:59,794
That they've been chosen with great care.

378
00:23:00,712 --> 00:23:01,713
Targeted.

379
00:23:02,881 --> 00:23:04,383
And not just disappeared.

380
00:23:05,009 --> 00:23:06,010
Destroyed.

381
00:23:07,177 --> 00:23:10,139
Wait, you're saying that
these planets disappearing,

382
00:23:10,222 --> 00:23:12,349
- that's connected to her?
- Yes.

383
00:23:13,225 --> 00:23:15,394
I've identified
the herald's energy signature

384
00:23:15,477 --> 00:23:17,812
and matched it to DA-773.

385
00:23:19,606 --> 00:23:21,025
She was there.

386
00:23:23,818 --> 00:23:24,945
She was at all of them.

387
00:23:25,445 --> 00:23:28,365
So you're saying this Galactus...

388
00:23:28,448 --> 00:23:30,409
Can do exactly what she says it can do.

