392
00:23:42,462 --> 00:23:44,089
The launch window is in 16.

393
00:23:44,173 --> 00:23:47,009
- Guys... Hey, guys.
- Like I said, 16 hours.

394
00:23:47,092 --> 00:23:48,153
I'll start the nav plot.

395
00:23:48,177 --> 00:23:49,178
Hey, guys...

396
00:23:49,261 --> 00:23:52,014
H, you wanna buzz the prep team
