397
00:23:52,097 --> 00:23:54,266
Uh, she spoke to me.
The herald. She spoke to me.

398
00:23:54,349 --> 00:23:55,850
She spoke to all of us, Johnny.

399
00:23:55,934 --> 00:23:57,436
Galactus, devouring...

400
