What did she say?

402
00:24:02,691 --> 00:24:04,651
Well, it was in her own language.
I don't know.

403
00:24:04,734 --> 00:24:06,111
Well, what were the context clues?

404
00:24:06,195 --> 00:24:08,113
Context. Space.

405
00:24:08,197 --> 00:24:09,906
And what was the tone?

406
00:24:09,990 --> 00:24:11,325
Angry? Threatening?

407
00:24:11,408 --> 00:24:13,452
No, no, no. Not at all. It was, uh...

408
00:24:15,245 --> 00:24:16,080
kind.

409
00:24:16,163 --> 00:24:17,164
Kind?

410
00:24:17,206 --> 00:24:18,290
Not kind. Warm.

411
00:24:18,373 --> 00:24:20,209
- Warm?
- I don't know. It was...

412
00:24:20,292 --> 00:24:22,586
- She was, like, right here.
- Mm-hmm.

413
00:24:22,669 --> 00:24:26,090
And I was looking into her beautiful face,

414
00:24:26,673 --> 00:24:28,592
and I saw stars,

415
00:24:28,675 --> 00:24:31,220
