416
00:24:31,303 --> 00:24:34,098
She spoke to me, and it was kind of, um...

417
00:24:34,181 --> 00:24:35,015
Warm?

418
00:24:35,099 --> 00:24:36,975
Kind. Kind?

419
00:24:37,059 --> 00:24:38,977
No. No. I get it.

420
00:24:39,644 --> 00:24:42,731
Johnny loves space. Johnny loves women.

421
00:24:42,814 --> 00:24:45,025
Now there's a literal naked space woman,

422
00:24:45,859 --> 00:24:47,253
