439
00:26:01,435 --> 00:26:02,602
The new space suits.

440
00:26:05,189 --> 00:26:06,856
It's flame-retardant.

441
00:26:06,940 --> 00:26:08,942
Maxed out oxygen supply, but...

442
00:26:09,025 --> 00:26:10,485
